Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: livedesktop
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: Bring your desktop wallpaper alive!
Home-page: https://github.com/olivopaolo/livedesktop
Author: Paolo Olivo
Author-email: olivopaolo@tiscali.it
License: GPLv3
Description: **livedesktop** periodically sends network requests to obtain the view of a public webcam; the obtained image is written to a target file, which is periodically refreshed.
        
        Configure your desktop wallpaper to slide show, and select the target folder in order to have the webcam view on your desktop.
